but at smaller stations the platforms are very low and you have to ascend several steep steps to board the train so be prepared if you have a large suitcase. generally passengers are friendly and will offer to help you with bulky luggage. smoking is not permitted in the seating or sleeping areas but is allowed in the vestibules at the end of each car. on the new crh trains, the guangzhou-kowloon shuttle train and the beijing suburban railway smoking is completely forbidden. smoking is banned inside station buildings apart from in designated smoking rooms, although these places are often 